'''

1.Python is Dynamically typed Programming language
2.In python While declearing variables we no need to menction DataTypes
3.Datatypes will be assignes by language based on values sotred in the variables at runtime.

Execution phase:
compiled time phase
Runtime time phase

Dynamically Types: 

{Variables.py(Source file) ----> language processer(Compiler)Byte Code(Variables.pyc)}COMPILED TIME PHASE---->{Python Virtual Machine(Interpeter)----> Machine Code(0's and 1's)}RUNTIME PHASE

At run time Data types will be assigned.

a = 10
b = 20

print("Addition of a and b :",a+b)

From the first line the Exection will start

At Compilation time the Errors Will be Checked
In python every thing is Objects.

We can change the values when ever we want.
